{"tid":2308100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前區議員 違規公屋洗樓 派發民政處物資","createTime":"2020-12-01T15:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T18:13:53.000Z","uid":55700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc895f956c5ec4f90732b547fbe8c142a70654a0","tid":2308100,"uid":55700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"觀塘民建聯落敗區議員 離奇有區會月曆派街坊 現任梁凱晴反未收到：想派都冇<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/XSZGCOQUMZD5JLE7NARGD47RGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FXSZGCOQUMZD5JLE7NARGD47RGE%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=7622853e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FXSZGCOQUMZD5JLE7NARGD47RGE%2F&h=64838340\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/XSZGCOQUMZD5JLE7NARGD47RGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n現任觀塘油塘東區議員龔振祺昨日（11月30日）接獲投訴，指該區<span class=\"red\">前區議員張琪騰</span>晚上<span class=\"red\">違規到公屋洗樓</span>，<span class=\"red\">不但派發民政處供應予觀塘區議員的月曆，更違反規定在派發物資上附帶個人宣傳品。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TWwJRqD5sfRQnY0vqiGr7K5OhkE=/511x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BRURAPM3MVGNJCMNR4FPBIZ5UA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTWwJRqD5sfRQnY0vqiGr7K5OhkE%3D%2F511x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBRURAPM3MVGNJCMNR4FPBIZ5UA.JPG&h=e66afb0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張琪騰回覆查詢時對於他所派發的月曆是否來自觀塘區議會，他拒絕正面回應，稱：「乜嘢要回應」，強調自己都只是將月曆派發予觀塘區居民，又自言不是以不法途徑取得有關物資，再被問到他以甚麼身份取得物資、以非區議員身份派發區議員物資時，他就稱：「我唔回應啦，唔該你！」，隨即匆匆掛線。<br />\n張琪騰回覆Now新聞台時則指，有關月曆是現任區議員分給他派發，可能民政處派發物資有先有後，又指街坊不在家，故此他留下聯絡方式。<br />\n<br />\n梁凱晴批評區議會資源若有過多，都應再分配予區議員派發，「唔係畀啲『無名無姓』嘅人」，又質疑有關月曆可能由現任建制派區議員轉交張派發；而即使派發，也應該遵守相關《運用區議會撥款守則》，不准在有關物品展示個人名稱等宣傳，重申落選人士派發區議會物資不合情理。"},{"pid":"bff9a4f795cad9d97892f65036d238db280aeb15","tid":2308100,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"佢點派的"},{"pid":"6fec4b2aa7a5c07ddeda806d8b0e99bbc07881d0","tid":2308100,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:13:53.000Z","msg":"成個政府真係核撚突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}